ige: Black Widow's Past to be Explored in Avengers 2 and Possible Solo Film|last=Couto|first=Anthony|website=[[IGN]]|date=February 12, 2014|access-date=February 13, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223230757/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/02/13/feige-black-widows-past-to-be-explored-in-avengers-2-and-possible-solo-film|archive-date=February 23, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PerlmanWidow\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cineplex.com/News/Screenwriter-Nicole-Perlman-gives-us-the-scoop-on-Guardians-Marvel-and-more|title=Screenwriter Nicole Perlman gives us the scoop on Guardians, Marvel, and more!|last=West|first=Rachel|website=[[Cineplex Entertainment|Cineplex]]|date=July 25, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728080621/http://www.cineplex.com/News/Screenwriter-Nicole-Perlman-gives-us-the-scoop-on-Guardians-Marvel-and-more|archive-date=July 28, 2014|access-date=July 26, 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"HayterRevive\">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a585310/x-mens-david-hayter-wants-to-revive-black-widow-film.html#~oL8zDz7mrR48fA|title=X-Men's David Hayter wants to revive Black Widow|website=[[Digital Spy]]|date=July 21, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723182057/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a585310/x-mens-david-hayter-wants-to-revive-black-widow-film.html#~oL8zDz7mrR48fA|archive-date=July 23, 2014|access-date=July 26, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"JohanssonApr2014\">{{cite web|url=http://screenrant.com/scarlett-johansson-talks-black-widow-solo-film/|title=Captain America 2 Interview: Scarlett Johansson Talks 'Black Widow' Solo Film|last=Keyes|first=Rob|website=[[Screen Rant]]|date=April 2014|access-date=July 26, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727083858/http://screenrant.com/scarlett-johansson-talks-black-widow-solo-film/|archive-date=July 27, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Marshall\">{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com